These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, indonesian
1. the indonesian is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the indonesian is between the mexican and the pakistani##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | indonesian | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, spy
1. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching spy movies##2
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | thriller | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, rock, disco
1. the fan of rock is between the fan of blues and the fan of disco##2
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | rock | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, bird, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | fish | hamster | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, coffee
1. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | sprite | mirinda | coffee |

 #################################

 
